item.title: Improving Architecture with Structure 101
item.description: I want to share with you yet another tool this one will help you with the architecture development. The tool is called Structure 101and you can download a trial version here. That’s right, this tool is not free, but it does it’s job really well and at the time I can’t think of a free alternative that would be just as good. If you do know any good alternative, please, do leave a comment.
